Package: ageTMP
Title: Age-Dependent Tumor Molecular Trajectory Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Nicole", "Tignor", email = "nicole.tignor@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Nicole Tignor
Maintainer: Nicole Tignor <nicole.tignor@gmail.com>
Description: Reproducibility-first framework for modeling and interpreting age-associated molecular trajectories in tumors relative to developmental or reference populations. The package supports age-dependent tumor molecular phenotype generation, tumor-normal trajectory comparison, trajectory visualization and divergence analysis, clustering, and downstream survival modeling including Cross-Population Survival Analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: readxl, stats, utils
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), ggplot2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
